languages.text: "Никакой это не Вольный Торговец, а переодетый блюститель! Зуб даю! Они что-то задумали, а нас за дураков держат!"
"That's not the Rogue Trader! It's a plainclothes enforcer! Well, more of a poshclothes one, really. Anyway, they're up to something and trying to play us for fools!"

languages.text: 「あれはローグトレーダーじゃない！私服のエンフォーサーだ！とにかく、連中は何かを企んでいる。俺らを馬鹿にしてるんだ！」
languages.original_text: "That's not the Rogue Trader! It's a plainclothes enforcer! Well, more of a poshclothes one, really. Anyway, they're up to something and trying to play us for fools!"

traits.locale_text: 「あれはローグトレーダーじゃない！私服のエンフォーサーだ！とにかく、連中は何かを企んでいる。俺らを馬鹿にしてるんだ！」

languages.text: “那个人根本不是行商浪人！只是个穿着便衣的执法者而已！呃，或者说是穿着华服的执法者。总之，那群人打算搞什么阴谋，想把我们当白痴耍！”
languages.original_text: "That's not the Rogue Trader! It's a plainclothes enforcer! Well, more of a poshclothes one, really. Anyway, they're up to something and trying to play us for fools!"

languages.text: "Das ist nicht {mf|der Freihändler|die Freihändlerin}! Das ist ein Enforcer in Zivil. Na ja, eher einer in Nobelklamotten. Wie auch immer, da ist etwas im Busch, und wir sind wieder die Idioten!"

languages.text: "O Hür Tacir değil! Sivil bir infazcı! Daha çok gösterişli giyinmiş gerçi. Her neyse, kesin peşinde olduğu bir şey var ve bizi aptal yerine koymaya çalışıyor!"
